{"type": "article", "id": 18076, "title": "叶子地毯", "description": "", "date": "2015-11-26T07:20:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606071224256W3YDoS5PEM4CmRN.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这组像树叶一样的地毯来自纽约设计师 Nao Tamura ，沿着中轴勾勒出细密的纹路，并不完全对称。有些地方还有疏密的不同关系，像是有缺陷的叶子，非常自然。设计师受到日本崇尚残缺之美的影响，让这片叶子地毯有一种简单的手工感。三种型号的地毯对应象牙白、灰绿色和橄榄绿。<a href=\"http://nanimarquina.com/news/quill-presentation/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122423CTcbufW7RSFOg83w.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122423rIH1BdZYqjGbpVxM.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122424aZotQBnSXGJHcVOx.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606071224244wTRNJzSlbkqemEI.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.94\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122425n5KRbQfN97JDxZvm.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74503311\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}